{"tid":1104951,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[純分享] 香港股股市行情表","createTime":"2019-04-13T13:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T10:39:51.000Z","uid":227995,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5795d354a047be4022290a8deca650490401dc3c","tid":1104951,"uid":227995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"今日執野見番08年1月1日生果報&quot;香港股股市行情表&quot;,<br />\n當時報紙仲會報導股票收市價.<br />\n<br />\n記得當年小弟啱啱畢業做野無耐開始學人買股票,<br />\n當時話專登留低08年第一日呢張B版財經版作個記錄, <br />\n10年後睇番當年既股價.<br />\n<br />\n當時仲以為係牛市緊, 其實已經熊一緊, 係金融海嘯.<br />\n當年都有27000幾點, 同而家唔係相差好遠.<br />\n不過個時大市成交好細, 得400幾億.<br />\n其實睇番各大藍籌股既股價, 相比依家都幾唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGLC6YA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGLC6YA.jpg&h=baa9167d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3egyFmj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3egyFmj.jpg&h=37d3f86c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n十大成交額第一係941, 成137蚊,<br />\n第二係2628, 40蚊; 第四係5號仔, 131蚊, <br />\n如今已不復當年勇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而內銀股同依家差唔多<br />\n <br />\n湊湊吓又諗起依家股王&quot;騰訊&quot;, <br />\n原來已經有, 收59蚊,<br />\n不過括住&quot;二百&quot;, 唔知咩意思?<br />\n個時有邊個會留意呢間公司呢?<br />\n如果個時買咗就發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fFCqwx0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfFCqwx0.jpg&h=9ebb7a53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又諗諗吓買咗十幾年股票, <br />\n其實係賺多, 係蝕多呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&quot;長線投資&quot; 真係好蝦人玩..."},{"pid":"6590c33cf708135f8a98e5861c0609df1d11d84f","tid":1104951,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"十年又過去..."},{"pid":"77fe8bf9c8b454b474ad03ca90f59c7c61dc9084","tid":1104951,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"